data.description: Have a spacious and bright new home before the new year! This four bedroom, 2.5 bath home, located in St. George school district has a great open layout. Entering the front door, you are greeted by the large living room with newer hardwood flooring and tall windows for lots of natural light. Heading down the hall, is the lovely kitchen, featuring maple cabinets, laminate counters, and a great island that stays. Appliances come with the house too! There's even a pantry, which is great for storage. The kitchen opens up into the family room, with a fireplace, making the home warm and cozy for those cooler winter evenings. There's an updated and modern powder bath too. Heading upstairs, is the large primary suite, featuring a walk in closet, and an ensuite bath, with double sinks, a walk in shower, and a soaking tub. Three large guest bedrooms, all with great closet space. Updated and charming full guest bath. There's even an extra loft area upstairs, that could be a great little place space, study, office, you name it! Second floor laundry too! The large full basement has tons of room for storage or for finishing down the line. Heading outside, is the paver patio, fire pit, and a large fenced in back yard. Great 2.5 car garage! Call today for your private showing!
